race.comment: ROMANTIC MISS (11) went forward last start over 1100m at Horsham and held on well for second, beaten half a length. Just missed at Ballarat prior and with Meech sticking rates well to break through.  LARKIN (3) did his best work late and beaten 1.5 lengths over 1009m at Yarra Valley when resuming from a spell. Presents fitter and he is one of the key runners. BUNDORAN (7) returns from a spell having her first run for a new yard. Fitter for a minor placing in a recent Horsham trial with race rider Bates aboard. Has the ability and will be naturally improved. TAGYOURIT (12) unraced 3yo filly who has trialled three times. Best trial form was when she won at Horsham on October 20. In the mix.
